---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Legal | MANGO Agency" activeNav="" lang="en">
  <section class="py-28 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4">Legal Notice</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary mb-16">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <!-- Privacy Policy -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8 uppercase">Privacy Policy</h2>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">1. Who We Are</h3>
            <p>MANGO Agency ("we", "us", "our") is a talent management agency specializing in content creator growth and monetization. We operate under the domain mangova.agency. For any privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@mangova.agency" class="text-primary underline">hello@mangova.agency</a>.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p class="mb-3">We collect information that you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Submit an application through our website form (name, email, social media handles, current metrics)</li>
              <li>Contact us via email or social media</li>
              <li>Enter into a service agreement with us</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">We do not collect personal information automatically through cookies or tracking scripts beyond basic analytics provided by our hosting provider (Vercel).</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>To evaluate your application and assess potential collaboration</li>
              <li>To communicate with you about our services</li>
              <li>To fulfill our contractual obligations if you become a client</li>
              <li>To improve our services and website</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h3>
            <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties except:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
              <li>With service providers necessary for our operations (e.g., hosting, communication tools)</li>
              <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
              <li>With your explicit consent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">5. Data Security</h3>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. We never require access to your platform credentials. Account management is conducted through secure, authorized employee access systems (e.g., Infloww).</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">6. Data Retention</h3>
            <p>Application data is retained for up to 12 months if you do not become a client. Client data is retained for the duration of the service agreement and up to 24 months after termination for legal and accounting purposes.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">7. Your Rights</h3>
            <p>You have the right to access, correct, delete, or export your personal data at any time. To exercise these rights, contact <a href="mailto:hello@mangova.agency" class="text-primary underline">hello@mangova.agency</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Terms of Service -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8 uppercase">Terms of Service</h2>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">1. Services</h3>
            <p>MANGO Agency provides content creator management services including but not limited to: chatting operations, marketing strategy, traffic generation, performance tracking, and operational optimization. All services are intended for individuals aged 18 and over.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">2. Application Process</h3>
            <p>Submitting an application does not guarantee acceptance. We reserve the right to decline applications at our discretion. The application process includes an evaluation call to determine mutual fit and align on objectives.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">3. Account Ownership</h3>
            <p>Clients retain 100% ownership and control of their accounts at all times. MANGO Agency operates as an extension of your brand, never as the owner. We utilize secure employee access systems and never require master credentials.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">4. Compensation</h3>
            <p>Our compensation model is performance-based. Specific terms, percentages, and payment schedules are agreed upon individually during the evaluation process and formalized in a separate service agreement.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">5. Termination</h3>
            <p>Either party may terminate the service agreement with reasonable prior notice. Upon termination, we provide a documented handover of all systems, data, and processes. There are no long-term lock-in contracts.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">6. Confidentiality</h3>
            <p>Both parties agree to maintain strict confidentiality regarding financial data, strategies, content, and any proprietary information shared during the collaboration.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">7. Disclaimer</h3>
            <p>Results presented on this website are based on data from projects managed by MANGO Agency and are not guaranteed. Growth outcomes vary depending on multiple factors including content quality, audience engagement, market conditions, and creator participation.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-on-surface font-bold text-base mb-3">8. Contact</h3>
            <p>For any legal inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@mangova.agency" class="text-primary underline">hello@mangova.agency</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
